Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.12,0:00:02.62,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}My name's Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.62,0:00:05.73,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}High school student Shin'ichi was\Nforced to take a drug that shrunk him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.73,0:00:08.53,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Although smaller, my mind remains\Nthat of a sharp detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.53,0:00:11.66,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Today's case is a two-part story\Naboard a luxury liner!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.66,0:00:13.63,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Think you can tell who did it just from Part 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.63,0:00:15.43,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}There's always only one truth!
